high_descs: Walk straight and reach the desk on the left side in which microwave oven is placed.
Take the tomato from the table which is next to the oven.
Now come in front of the microwave.
Open the oven and put the tomato inside the oven and close the door. After few seconds, open the oven and take the tomato out and then close the oven door.
Take a right turn and walk towards the countertop on the right side.
Put the tomato on the countertop which is next to the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put the Tomato on the CounterTop
